@CrossOrigin	//It help to enable the resources

		listofProduct.add(new Product(1, "Laptop", 100000, "https://encrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com/shopping?q=tbn:ANd9GcStyUqmRZj9nV--4CUeggkEaxPF60K_1GxmrZVqyq0H1Smdy15bzLd13-E8sB9Yrb3SlzBeQWQ-Tg&usqp=CAc"));

}
